{"tid":186892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"打工仔切身問題 問勞工法例","createTime":"2017-04-04T13:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T15:34:52.000Z","uid":103315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"adface0b99fd428ae7f2d994edf37b69da266a4d","tid":186892,"uid":103315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"份工冇試用期 一返工就直接開波一個月通知期<br />\n<br />\n但係老細有冇權係返工頭三個月因為放法定假期 同 公眾假期 而扣人工 真係完全唔清楚"},{"pid":"9bd68132ecfb7043ddea3aa7f402580f96056b61","tid":186892,"uid":66928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"直接打去勞工處問比較好&hellip;"},{"pid":"73446132c9773087f31fd0fee465408a8f8be343","tid":186892,"uid":12233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:06:51.000Z","msg":"頭3個月無紅日/勞工假<br />\n<br />\n利申:HR"},{"pid":"db7aec65430d56d0487a40952d892f1a07068473","tid":186892,"uid":60156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a0fsjt6b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa0fsjt6b&h=00d289b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先，係頭個月返工係無一個月通知<br />\n第二，以我理解應該係法定假期一定要比你放，公眾假期就唔一定有..<br />\n詳細打去問勞工處"},{"pid":"37886fe486fa142c6219871b3fc197053514df45","tid":186892,"uid":17684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"其實好睇間公司點做。法例上係無，但公司可提供優於法例上既褔利俾員工。<br />\n<br />\n樓主個case，一開波就無就用期，換言之即係公司正式員工，咁既情況下，佢應該可以享有公眾假期人工。"},{"pid":"19fbb3f220bfe3430a2618bffa4478d3a3cfd040","tid":186892,"uid":103315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都唔想 但係個老細好古惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋我果行都好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c9c0dc81339ab7ca0ec4098bf9cd26258f3226","tid":186892,"uid":23629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0